tions%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20cost%20him%20a%20poll%20ticket%20this%20time.%20The%20BJP%20instead%20fielded%20his%20son%20Karan%2C%20also%20a%20wrestling%20administrator.%20His%20other%20son%2C%20Pratik%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20is%20MLA%20from%20Gonda%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20from%20the%20accident%20site%20show%20the%20SUV%20with%20%26quot%3Bpolice%20escort%26quot%3B%20written%20on%20the%20rear%20windscreen%2C%20suggesting%20it%20is%20part%20of%20a%20VIP%20convoy.%C2%A0The%20car's%20number%20is%20UP32HW1800%20and%20it%20is%20said%20to%20be%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Nandini%20Nagar%20educational%20institute%20run%20by%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh's%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20complainant%20Chanda%20Begum%20has%20said%20that%20around%209%20am%20today%2C%20her%2017-year-old%20son%20Rehan%20and%2024-year-old%20nephew%20Shahzad%20were%20out%20on%20a%20bike%20to%20buy%20medicines%20when%20the%20speeding%20SUV%20coming%20from%20the%20opposite%20side%20hit%20the%20two-wheeler.%20Both%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%C2%A0A%2060-year-old%20woman%2C%20identified%20as%20Sita%20Devi%2C%20was%20injured%20and%20has%20been%20hospitalised.%20A%20huge%20crowd%20gathered%20at%20the%20site%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20as%20family%20members%20of%20the%20victims%20demanded%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20arrested%20the%20driver%20and%20seized%20the%20SUV.%20There%20is%20no%20confirmation%20yet%20on%20whether%20Karan%20Bhushan%20Singh%20was%20travelling%20with%20the%20cavalcade%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident.%C2%A0Senior%20police%20officer%20Radheysham%20Rai%20said%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20victims%20have%20been%20sent%20for%20autopsy%20and%20further%20probe%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20car%2C%20with%20the%20number%20UP32HW1800%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Nandini%20Nagar%20educational%20institure%20run%20by%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh's%20f