%20on%20June%202%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20last%20leg%20of%20polling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20registrar%2C%20while%20refusing%20the%20plea%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20given%20liberty%20to%20move%20trial%20court%20for%20regular%20bail%2C%20and%20hence%20this%20petition%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20maintainable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20had%20sought%20an%20extension%20on%20medical%20ground%20and%20requested%20the%20court%20for%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20health%20complications%20and%20increased%20risk%20signs%2C%20a%20medical%20examination%20is%20necessary%20to%20protect%20him%20from%20possible%20long-term%20harm%20to%20during%20his%20prison%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20who%20is%20representing%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20said%20in%20the%20petition.%20He%20had%20also%20stressed%20that%20the%20AAP%20leader%20will%20remain%20%26quot%3Bvisible%20and%20available%20in%20public%26quot%3B%20while%20out%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20risk%20of%20fleeing%20the%20legal%20process%20and%20conditions%20set%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20(for%20interim%20bail)%20have%20been%20followed...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20on%20May%2010%20granted%2021-day%20interim%20bail%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20excise%20policy%20'scam'%2C%20to%20enable%20him%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20directed%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20to%20surrender%20on%20June%202%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20last%20phase%20of%20the%20seven-phase%20poll%20gets%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20believes%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20drafting%20the%20now-scrapped%20policy%20and%20seeking%20bribes%2C%20or%20kickbacks%2C%20in%20return%20for%20liquor%20licences.%20The%20agency%20has%20claimed%20the%20AAP%20received%20kickbacks%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20that%20was%20then%20used%20to%20fund%20its%20Goa%20and%20Punjab%20election%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20have%20refused%20all%20charges%20and%20called%20the%20arrest%20and%20case%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20vendetta%26quot%3B%2C%20coming%20as%20it%20did%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20election.%20The%20arrest%20also%20triggered%20a%20political%20spat%20between%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20which%20is%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20of%20which%20the%20AAP%20is%20a%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716966960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4t8b8ev8_arvind-kejriwal-ani-650_650x400_04_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwals-plea-for-extension-of-bail-wont-be-heard-by-supreme-court-5769345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20not%20hear%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20request%20seeking%20a%207-day%20extension%20of%20his%20interim%20bail%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwals-plea-for-extension-of-bail-wont-be-heard-by-supreme-court-5769345%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwals-plea-for-extension-of-bail-wont-be-heard-by-supreme-court-5769345%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwals-plea-for-extension-of-bail-wont-be-heard-by-supreme-court-5769345%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah%20Explains%20Why%20PM%20Modi's%20Kashmir%20Policy%20Has%20Been%20A%20Success%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20during%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20said%20that%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20helped%20strengthen%20democracy%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20He%20said%20the%20move%20sent%20a%20clear%20message%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Valley%20that%20they%20are%20a%20part%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20ji%20scrapped%20Article%20370%20and%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20Valley%20that%20you%20are%20a%20part%20of%20India%20and%20India%20belongs%20to%20you%2C%20you%20belong%20to%20India.%20I%20believe%20because%20of%20this%20the%20foundation%20of%20democracy%20there%20got%20stronger%2C%20and%20not%20just%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20even%20panchayat%20polls%20there%20there%20was%2090%20per%20cent%20voting.%20I%20believe%20it%20is%20a%20huge%20achievement%20and%20every%20Indian%20should%20welcome%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20during%20a%20conversation%20with%20NDTV's%20editor-in-chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20been%20so%20successful%20in%20the%20region%20that%20even%20members%20of%20separatist%20organisations%20are%20now%20casting%20their%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20of%20Jamaat%20e-Islami%20and%20Hurriyat%20voted%20and%20said%20they%20voted%20under%20Indian%20Constitution%20since%20there%20is%20no%20J%26amp%3BK%20Constitution.%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20now%20under%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20so%20I%20believe%20Narendra%20Modi's%20Kashmir%20policy%20was%20successful.%20For%20so%20many%20years%2C%20Kashmir%20was%20being%20governed%20through%20appeasement%20politics%20but%20not%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Home%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20is%20hoping%20to%20win%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term.%20Last%20phase%20of%20polling%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20on%20June%201%2C%20and%20results%20will%20be%20declared%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20about%20BJP's%20pitch%20of%20winning%20400%2B%20seats%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20won%20the%202014%20elections%20under%20Narendra%20Modi's%20leadership%20on%20the%20slogan%20of%20absolute%20majority%2C%20many%20political%20analysts%20from%20Delhi%20had%20said%20this%20was%20not%20possible.%20But%20we%20got%20absolute%20majority.%20Then%2C%20in%202019%2C%20when%20we%20gave%20the%20slogan%20of%20'300%20plus'%2C%20people%20said%20it%20is%20not%20possible.%20People%20are%20saying%20the%20same%20this%20time.%20But%20I%20think%20they%20will%20believe%20us%20in%20the%20next%20election%20before%20'400%20par'%20is%20happening%20this%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716966780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F8ol4npp_amit-shah_625x300_29_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-amit-shah-explains-why-pm-modis-kashmir-policy-has-been-a-success-5770009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20during%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20said%20that%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20helped%20strengthen%20democracy%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-amit-shah-explains-why-pm-modis-kashmir-policy-has-been-a-success-5770009%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-amit-shah-explains-why-pm-modis-kashmir-policy-has-been-a-success-5770009%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-amit-shah-explains-why-pm-modis-kashmir-policy-has-been-a-success-5770009%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%203.5%20cr%20seized%20in%20ED%20searches%20in%20Punjab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716966543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110526191%2Cimgsize-2007675.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frs-3-5-cr-seized-by-ed-in-searches-at-jalandhar-and-other-places-in-punjab%2Farticleshow%2F110526115.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%8BIt%20has%20come%20to%20light%20that%20illegal%20mining%20activities%20were%20taking%20place%20on%20land%20that%20had%20been%20previously%20seized%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20notorious%20Bhola%20drug%20case.%20The%20case%20is%20currently%20at%20a%20critical%20stage%20of%20trial%20before%20the%20Special%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frs-3-5-cr-seized-by-ed-in-searches-at-jalandhar-and-other-places-in-punjab%2Farticleshow%2F110526115.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Millions%20Share%20'All%20Eyes%20On%20Rafah'%20On%20Instagram%3A%20What%20The%20Image%20Means%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20Israeli%20strikes%20that%20killed%20at%20least%2045%20Palestinians%2C%20including%20many%20children%2C%20in%20tents%20full%20of%20displaced%20people%20in%20Gaza's%20Rafah%20have%20drawn%20widespread%20condemnation%20from%20several%20countries%20and%20human%20rights%20groups.%20The%20Tal%20as-Sultan%20area%2C%20a%20designated%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20zone%26quot%3B%20in%20northwest%20of%20Rafah%20city%2C%20was%20hit%20by%20at%20least%20eight%20Israeli%20missiles%2C%20Al%20Jazeera%20reported%20quoting%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%20home%20to%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20displaced%20Palestinians%20from%20all%20over%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20Rafah%20came%20under%20Israeli%20ground%20and%20air%20offensive%20on%20Sunday%2C%20despite%20widespread%20international%20concern%20over%20civilian%20casualties.%20The%20attack%20also%20left%20several%20tents%20on%20fire%2C%20which%20then%20swept%20through%20the%20area%2C%20killing%20more%20people.%20A%20fuel%20tank%20explosion%2C%20triggered%20by%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%2C%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20fire%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Ftech%2Finternet%2F-eyes-rafah-image-shared-millions-instagram-rcna154380%C2%A0%5C%22%3ENBC%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3E%26quot%3BAll%20Eyes%20On%20Rafah%26quot%3B%3A%20What%20the%20image%20depicts%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20visuals%20of%20charred%20bodies%20and%20those%20with%20severe%20injuries%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%2C%20an%20image%20with%20text%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20Eyes%20on%20Rafah%26quot%3B%2C%20started%20trending.%20The%20campaign%2C%20spearheaded%20by%20activists%20and%20humanitarian%20groups%2C%20aims%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20where%20people%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20live%20in%20cramped%20refugee%20camps%20with%20no%20humanitarian%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20image%20shows%20tents%20at%20a%20camp%20arranged%20to%20form%20the%20words%20%26quot%3BAll%20Eyes%20on%20Rafah%26quot%3B%2C%20urging%20people%20not%20to%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20situation%20in%20Gaza's%20southernmost%20city%2C%20where%20approximately%201.5%20million%20people%20have%20sought%20shelter%20after%20fleeing%20Israeli%20bombings.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EIs%20the%20image%20real%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20image%20might%20be%20one%20of%20the%20first%20artificial%20intelligence-generated%20viral%20activism%20pictures.%20According%20to%20Marc%20Owen%20Jones%2C%20who%20studies%20misinformation%2C%20the%20image%20%26quot%3Blooks%26quot%3B%20like%20it%20was%20created%20by%20AI.%20Not%20looking%20very%20real%2C%20having%20odd%20shadows%2C%20and%20the%20tent%20camp%20being%20unnaturally%20symmetrical%20are%20some%20of%20the%20signs%20that%20it's%20an%20AI-generated%20image%2C%20NBC%20reported.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EWhere%20does%20the%20phrase%20come%20from%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20slogan%20is%20said%20to%20have%20originated%20from%20a%20statement%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealthpolicy-watch.news%2Fall-eyes-on-rafah-says-head-of-who-office-for-occupied-palestine-territories%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3ERick%20Peeperkorn%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20director%20of%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization's%20Office%20of%20the%20Occupied%20Palestinian%20Territories.%20He%20made%20the%20comment%20in%20February%2C%20shortly%20after%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20ordered%20an%20evacuation%20plan%20for%20Rafah%20ahead%20of%20attacks%20aimed%20at%20what%20the%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20then%20claimed%20were%20the%20last%20remaining%20strongholds%20of%20the%20militant%20group%20Hamas.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EHow%20the%20image%20spread%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSupport%20groups%20like%20Save%20the%20Children%2C%20Oxfam%2C%20Americans%20for%20Justice%20in%20Palestine%20Action%2C%20Jewish%20Voice%20for%20Peace%20and%20the%20Palestine%20Solidarity%20Campaign%20have%20also%20adopted%20the%20slogan.%20On%20social%20media%2C%20the%20hashtag%20%23AllEyesOnRafah%20has%20garnered%20over%201%2C95%2C000%20posts%20with%20millions%20of%20views.%20It%20was%20also%20trending%20on%20Instagram%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20with%20nearly%201%2C00%2C000%20additional%20posts%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20image%20has%20been%20shared%20over%2029%20million%20times%20on%20Instagram%20in%20less%20than%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupport%20for%20the%20campaign%20surged%20globally%2C%20with%20Indian%20celebrities%2C%20including%20Varun%20Dhawan%2C%20Madhuri%20Dixit%2C%20Aly%20Goni%2C%20Samantha%20Ruth%20Prabhu%2C%20Tripti%20Dimri%20etc%20sharing%20the%20identical%20%26quot%3BAll%20Eyes%20on%20Rafah%26quot%3B%20image%20on%20their%20Instagram%20stories.%20Internationally%2C%20figures%20like%20Australian%20cricket%20pla