.5%20crore%20Porsche.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-member%20committee%20led%20by%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20state's%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20department%20will%20inquire%20into%20the%20roles%20of%20Dr%20LN%20Danwade%2C%20who%20released%20the%20teen%20on%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20of%20the%20horrific%20incident%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-the-7-conditions-listed-in-bail-order-of-pune-teen-who-killed-2-techies-5719922%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterms%20included%20writing%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20road%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2015%2C000.%20These%20terms%20were%20later%20modified%20-%20after%20widespread%20public%20outrage%20and%20the%20cops%20indicating%20they%20would%20charge%20the%20boy%20as%20an%20adult%20-%20and%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20a%20remand%20home%20till%20June%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbail-of-pune-teen-who-killed-2-techies-with-porsche-cancelled-5722458%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPune%20Teen%20Who%20Killed%202%20Sent%20To%20Remand%20Home%20Till%20June%205%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20members%20on%20the%20state's%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%3B%20two%20are%20named%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20and%20the%20third%20is%20drawn%20from%20the%20judiciary.%20The%20committee%20will%20check%20if%20applicable%20legal%20provisions%20were%20followed%20while%20granting%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20will%20be%20submitted%20next%20week%2C%20Prashant%20Narnawre%2C%20the%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Commissioner%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pune%20Porsche%20crash%20case%20has%20taken%20several%20murky%20turns%20since%20the%20teen%20-%20four%20months%20shy%20of%20legal%20driving%20age%20and%20nearly%20eight%20years%20shy%20of%20legal%20drinking%20age%20-%20boy%20ran