%20the%20Engagement%20Platoon%20Commander%20with%20the%20Indian%20Rapid%20Deployment%20Battalion%20till%20April%202024.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20Radhika%20Sen%20is%20the%20second%20Indian%20peacekeeper%20to%20receive%20the%20Military%20Gender%20Advocate%20of%20the%20Year%20Award.%20Before%20Ms%20Sen%2C%20Major%20Suman%20Gawani%20was%20recognised%20for%20her%20service%20with%20the%20UN%20Mission%20in%20South%20Sudan.%20She%20was%20honoured%20in%202019.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4.%20Among%20the%206%2C063%20Indian%20personnel%20deployed%20in%20UN%20peacekeeping%20operations%2C%20Ms%20Sen%20served%20alongside%201%2C954%20individuals%20within%20MONUSCO%2C%20of%20which%2032%20were%20women.%20Her%20work%20created%20safe%20spaces%20for%20women%20to%20unite%20and%20discuss%20issues.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn5.%20Ms%20Sen%20led%20peacekeeping%20efforts%20in%20the%20eastern%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo%20(DRC)%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20gender%20equality%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN.%20She%20organised%20programs%20like%20English%20classes%20for%20kids%20and%20health%20and%20vocational%20training%20for%20adults.%20Ms%20Sen%20also%20established%20Community%20Alert%20Networks%2C%20aiding%20conflict-affected%20communities%20in%20North%20Kivu.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716964380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fatra6qu8_major-radhika-sen_625x300_29_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-radhika-sen-indian-army-major-to-get-un-award-for-gender-advocacy-5769115%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Major%20Radhika%20Sen%2C%20who%20served%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20peacekeeping%20mission%20in%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%2C%20will%20be%20honoured%20with%20the%20prestigious%202023%20Military%20Gender%20Advocate%20of%20the%20Year%20Award.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-radhika-sen-indian-army-maj