gineer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20hopped%20quite%20a%20bit.%20I%20optimized%20for%20money%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-engineer-meta-sap-salesforce-tesla-amazon-linkedin-jobs-branding-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20his%20compensation%20journey%20since%20graduating%20from%20university%20in%202017.%20His%20career%20path%20has%20brought%20him%20to%20Tesla%2C%20SAP%2C%20Salesforce%2C%20and%20his%20current%20role%20at%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d9414a6-d2c5-4cef-ac4c-5ac509c344ec%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETesla%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPandey%20joined%20Tesla%20in%20February%202018%20after%20his%20master's%20in%20computer%20science.%20He%20got%20a%20standard%20new%20graduate%20offer%20for%20software%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20offered%20%24150%2C000%20a%20year%20for%20a%20base%20salary%2C%20restricted%20stock%20units%2C%20and%20an%20annual%20bonus.%20He%20negotiated%20his%20sign-on%20bonus%20from%20%248%2C000%20to%20%2412%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20months%20after%20starting%2C%20he%20was%20laid%20off%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-to-layoff-up-to-9-of-its-employees-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4%2C000%20other%20employees.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20he%20needed%20a%20work%20visa%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20stay%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20had%20about%20three%20months%20to%20find%20a%20new%20role.%20He%20began%20applying%20and%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20SAP%20at%20the%20end%20of%20July%2C%20seven%20weeks%20after%20he%20started%20looking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d3ea4db6-c954-4bbc-af41-ca07a2ce3649%5C%22%3ESAP%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPandey%20joined%20the%20company%20in%20September%20in%20a%20new%20graduate%20role%2C%20like%20at%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20competing%20offers%20so%20I%20did%20not%20have%20much%20leverage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20negotiated%20base%20by%206%25%20and%20sign%20on%20by%2020%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20up%20to%20%24165%2C000%20annually%2C%20plus%20a%20%2412%2C000%20sign-on%20bonus.%20Pandey%20spent%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year%20at%20SAP%20and%20received%20an%20annual%20performance-related%20appraisal%20of%205%25%2C%20which%20brought%20his%20compensation%20to%20%24173%2C250.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriends%20spoke%20highly%20of%20Salesforce's%20company%20culture%2C%20and%20he%20thought%20he%20might%20be%20better%20compensated%20there.%20After%20a%20little%20over%20a%20year%20at%20SAP%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217ca47d9-09e2-456b-9435-81c8f3eab5f9%5C%22%3ESalesforce%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20moved%20to%20Salesforce%2C%20joining%20in%20a%20slightly%20more%20senior%20software%20role%20from%20his%20last%20role%20at%20SAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce%20offered%20Pandey%20a%2030%25%20increase%20on%20his%20total%20compensation%2C%20bringing%20the%20package%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eabout%20%24190%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20base%20salary%20was%20about%20%24150%2C000%2C%20stocks%20would%20amount%20to%20%2417%2C500%20per%20year%2C%20and%20his%20annual%20bonus%20was%20%2415%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20accepting%20the%20offer%2C%20he%20negotiated%20with%20Salesforce.%20That%20netted%20him%20a%20%2410%2C000%20sign-on%20bonus%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20hadn't%20offered%20one%20at%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20make%20sure%20to%20negotiate%20because%20there's%20always%20room%20from%20when%20they%20give%20you%20the%20initial%20offer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20time%20they're%20willing%20to%20go%2015%25%20or%2020%25%20higher%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20miss%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20suggests%20that%20all%20candidates%20negotiate%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20have%20leverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20competing%20offers%2C%20if%20you%20have%20pending%20interviews%2C%20all%20these%20kinds%20of%20things%20%E2%80%94%20then%20definitely%20negotiate.%20You%20can%20increase%20the%20compensation%20between%2020%25%20to%2030%25%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPandey%20was%20promoted%20at%20Salesforce%20after%2015%20months%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20got%20a%2020%25%20bump%20from%20his%20previous%20pay%2C%20bringing%20his%20total%20to%20around%20%24240%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20role%20moved%20him%20from%20software%20engineer%20to%20senior%20software%20engineer.%20He%20led%20projects%20with%20two%20to%20three%20engineers%20and%20worked%20with%20product%20managers%20and%20customers.%20He%20also%20found%20that%20his%20work%20had%20more%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20years%20at%20Salesforce%2C%20he%20applied%20to%20Meta%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228819dff8-1337-4f29-841b-7e6208fa72d5%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20Meta%20the%20same%20year%20he%20became%20a%20senior%20software%20engineer.%20It%20was%20still%20a%20vertical%20move%20because%20of%20the%20different%20ways%20Salesforce%20and%20Meta%20establish%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20significant%20thing%20happened%20in%20my%20career%20when%20I%20made%20the%20move%20from%20Salesforce%20to%20Meta%2C%20which%20was%20close%20to%20almost%2080-90%25%20hike%26quot%3B%20in%20pay%2C%20Pandey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20time%20he%20applied%20to%20Meta%2C%20Pandey%20also%20applied%20to%20TikTok%2C%20LinkedIn%2C%20and%20two%20other%20companies.%20He%20used%20offers%20from%20these%20companies%20to%20negotiate%20his%20compensation%20at%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20very%20transparent%20that%20you%20have%20other%20offers%2C%20even%20if%20you%20have%20interviews%20going%20on%20mention%20those%2C%20because%20it's%20also%20leverage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20It%20signals%20to%20the%20recruiter%20that%20they%20have%20to%20move%20fast%20and%20work%20with%20your%20parameters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20other%20offers%20meant%20that%20Meta's%20recruiters%20tried%20to%20match%20base%20salary%20and%20restricted%20stock%20units%20from%20the%20highest%20of%20all%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20being%20transparent%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPandey%20said%20it%20is%20important%20to%20be%20proactive%20and%20research%20how%20compensation%20works%20in%20different%20companies.%20For%20example%2C%20candidates%20should%20compare%20how%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Estocks%20are%20refreshed%2C%20he%20said.%20A%20refresher%20is%20when%20the%20stock%20option%20portion%20of%20an%20employee's%20compensation%20is%20updated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20negotiated%20my%20sign-on%20bonus%20and%20said%2C%20'Hey%2C%20at%20Salesforce%2C%20I'll%20be%20leaving%20my%2030%20to%2040k%20of%20annual%20bonus%20if%20I%20join%20you.%20Can%20you%20help%20me%20accommodate%20that%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPandey%20was%20offered%20%24520%2C000%20in%20annual%20pay%20in%20that%202021%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20currently%20a%20senior%20software%20engineer%20at%20Meta's%20Menlo%20Park%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20offer%20letters%2C%20employment%20history%2C%20and%20Meta%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20tech%2C%20finance%2C%20or%20consulting%20and%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20compensation%20journey%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ashubhangigoel%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eshubhangigoel%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-software-engineer-negotiated-salary-big-tech-meta-tesla-salesforce-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C