20the%20company%20and%20years%20of%20legal%20issues%20between%20the%20designer%20and%20her%20former%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Friday%2C%20a%20Delaware%20bankruptcy%20judge%20approved%20a%20settlement%20agreement%20between%20the%20pair%20that%20gives%20Gutman%20her%20name%2C%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20accounts%2C%20and%20all%20IP%20associated%20with%20the%20Hayley%20Paige%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20created%20a%20timeline%20to%20explain%20how%20the%20problems%20between%20Gutman%20and%20JLM%20arose%2C%20their%20messy%20legal%20battle%2C%20and%20the%20settlement%20that%20brought%20it%20all%20to%20a%20close.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20July%202011%2C%20wedding-dress%20designer%20Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20signed%20an%20employment%20agreement%20with%20fashion%20company%20JLM%20Couture.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fea31caedf8920018093ebf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20was%20in%20business%20with%20JLM%20Couture%20from%202011%20to%202020.%3Cp%3ESlaven%20Vlasic%20%2F%20Stringer%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHayley%20Paige%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20full%20name%20is%20Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20%E2%80%94%20began%20her%20journey%20to%20becoming%20a%20household%20bridal%20designer%20in%202011%2C%20when%20she%20signed%20an%20employment%20contract%20with%20JLM%20Couture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman's%20agreement%20with%20JLM%20granted%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bthe%20exclusive%20world-wide%20right%20and%20license%20to%20use%20her%20name%20'Hayley'%2C%20'Paige'%2C%20'Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman'%2C%20'Hayley%20Gutman'%2C%20'Hayley%20Paige'%2C%20or%20any%20derivative%20thereof%20%5B...%5D%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20design%2C%20manufacture%2C%20marketing%20and%2For%20sale%20of%20bridal%20clothing%2C%20bridal%20accessories%2C%20and%20related%20bridal%20and%20wedding%20items%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20December%202020%20complaint%20filed%20by%20the%20company's%20attorneys%20and%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJD7CIbn7UN%2F%5C%22%3Ean%20Instagram%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20was%2025%20when%20she%20signed%20the%20agreement%20and%20did%20not%20have%20a%20lawyer%20review%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20April%206%2C%202012%2C%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20account%20was%20launched.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayleypaige%20insta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ff4c4c56d61c10019ccdcf4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20page.%3Cp%3E%40misshayleypaige%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BAbout%26quot%3B%20page%20for%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmisshayleypaige%2F%5C%22%3E%40misshayleypaige%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Instagram%2C%20the%20account%20was%20created%20on%20April%206%2C%202012.%20(Two%20years%20later%2C%20in%202014%2C%20a%20Pinterest%20with%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20handle%20was%20also%20created%2C%20according%20to%20JLM's%20complaint.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20said%20she%20created%20the%20Instagram%20account%20in%20a%20press%20release%20provided%20to%20Business%20Insider%20and%20a%20video%20posted%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fallthatglittersonthegram%2F%5C%22%3Eseparate%20Instagram%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%20separate%20press%20release%20provided%20to%20BI%2C%20howe