e%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20JLM%20challenged%20Gutman's%20claims%20in%20a%20press%20statement.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20gutman%20video%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fea477aedf8920018093f0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20denied%20Gutman's%20claims%20since%20her%20video%20went%20viral.%3Cp%3EHayley%20Paige%20Gutman%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Gutman's%20announcement%20went%20viral%2C%20JLM%20released%20a%20press%20statement%20on%20December%2022%2C%202020%2C%20addressing%20the%20designer's%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20release%20challenged%20Gutman's%20claims%20that%20she%20owned%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20account%20and%20denied%20that%20Gutman%20could%20not%20post%20anything%20on%20the%20page.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-wedding-dress-designer-hayley-paige-banned-from-instagram-account-2020-12%5C%22%3EJLM%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0at%20the%20time%20that%20Gutman%20was%20not%20barred%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20accessing%20the%20brand's%20social%20media%20accounts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20however%2C%20a%20representative%20for%20Gutman%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20December%2027%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20temporary%20court%20order%20currently%20requires%20the%20written%20approval%20of%20CEO%20Joseph%20Murphy%2C%20not%20the%20brand%2C%20which%20speaks%20to%20the%20level%20of%20personal%20control%20he%20demands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20employee%20of%20JLM%20and%20has%20no%20interest%20whatsoever%20in%20posting%20their%20brand%20messaging%20to%20her%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20representative%20added%2C%20speaking%20of%20Gutman.%20%26quot%3BMy%20client%20is%20confident%20that%20her%20Instagram%20and%2