26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20response%20is%20my%20first%20opportunity%20to%20describe%20to%20the%20Court%20the%20misrepresentations%20and%20false%20claims%20that%20JLM%20Couture%20made%20in%20their%20emergency%20filing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20upon%20review%20of%20all%20of%20the%20facts%2C%20justice%20will%20be%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20shared%20the%20news%20of%20the%20response%20with%20her%20followers%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJ9oROBnLnM%2F%5C%22%3E%20an%20Instagram%20video%20on%20January%2012%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20she%20even%20added%20a%20link%20to%20the%20lawsuit%20to%20the%20bio%20of%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20Instagram%20page%2C%20allowing%20her%20followers%20to%20look%20at%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20you%20to%20take%20this%20journey%20along%20with%20me%2C%20and%20I%20have%20always%20valued%20transparency%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20why%20she%20added%20the%20link.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%202021%2C%20JLM%20filed%20a%20memorandum%20in%20support%20of%20its%20temporary%20restraining%20order.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20gutman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F600f0533cf23090019e9720f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221503%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20doubled%20down%20on%20its%20claims.%3Cp%3EMireya%20Acierto%20%2F%20Contributor%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20filed%20papers%20directly%20refuting%20the%20claims%20Gutman%20made%20against%20the%20company%20in%20her%20response%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memorandum%20doubled%20down%20on%20JLM's%20stance%20that%20Gutman%20was%20never%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20existence%20of%20personal%20posts%20on%