LM%20argued%20Gutman's%20social-media%20activity%20at%20the%20time%20breached%20that%20clause%2C%20since%20it%20had%20led%20bridal%20stores%20to%20stop%20working%20with%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20BI%20reached%20out%20to%20Gutman's%20team%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20memorandum%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20refuted%20JLM's%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM's%20latest%20claims%2C%20like%20their%20earlier%20ones%2C%20are%20full%20of%20assertions%20that%20are%20unsupported%20by%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20fail%20to%20address%20the%20evidence%20we%20presented%20to%20the%20Court%2C%20and%20we%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20being%20heard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20took%20place%20on%20February%204%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20March%205%2C%202021%2C%20JLM%20was%20granted%20a%20preliminary%20injunction%20against%20Gutman.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20gutman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6047a0c244d8e300117b9d60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20was%20granted%20a%20preliminary%20injunction.%3Cp%3ED%20Dipasupil%20%2F%20Contributor%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month%20of%20deliberation%2C%20a%20judge%20ruled%20in%20JLM's%20favor%2C%20as%20stated%20in%20a%20JLM%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJudge%20Swain%20found%20that%20JLM%20demonstrated%20a%20clear%20likelihood%20of%20success%20in%20proving%20Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20breached%20her%20employment%20contract%20and%20infringed%20the%20company's%20trademark%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20prevented%20Gutman%20from%20using%20any%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts%20or%20Hayley%20Paige%20trademarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Murphy%20continues%20to%20recognize%20and%20value%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20talent%20and%20remains%20hopeful%20that%20JLM%20and%20Ms.%20Gutman%20can%20reconcile%20their%20differences%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20ruling%20was%20a%20preliminary%20injunction%2C%20an%20additional%20hearing%20was%20held%20at%20a%20later%20date%20to%20examine%20the%20legal%20issues%20between%20JLM%20and%20Gutman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20disappointed%20in%20JLM's%20actions%20but%20determined%20to%20look%20to%20the%20future%20rather%20than%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20regarding%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20taken%20my%20name%2C%20and%20my%20social%20media%20for%20now%2C%20but%20JLM's%20business%20is%20built%20on%20the%20goodwill%20of%20amazing%20women%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20they%20will%20be%20accountable%20to%20these%20women%20for%20what%20they%20have%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20announced%20she%20would%20be%20changing%20her%20professional%20name%20on%20Instagram%20on%20March%208%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60479ae144d8e300117b9d37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20decided%20to%20change%20her%20professional%20name.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2Fallthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20Gutman%20announced%20on%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20Instagram%20account%20that%20she%20would%20be%20changing%20her%20name%20so%20she%20could%20continue%20to%20do%20business%20unassociated%20with%20JLM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20may%20have%20lost%20this%20round%20in%20court%2C%20but%20the%20bigger%20story%20is%20about%20a%20'girl%20you%20might%20know%2C'%20who%20is%20determined%20to%20pave%20her%20own%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMKY9APH5EZ%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20video%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20refuse%20to%20be%20nameless%2C%20and%20I%20refuse%20to%20be%20jobless.%20Since%20they%20have%20taken%20my%20name%2C%20I've%20decided%20to%20change%20it%2C%20officially%20and%20professionally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20be%20reduced%20by%20what%20has%20been%20taken%20from%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20had%20not%20picked%20her%20new%20professional%20name%20yet%2C%20and%20she%20asked%20her%20followers%20to%20help%20her%20choose%20a%20moniker%20in%20the%20video.%20She%20requested%20they%20choose%20a%20name%20that%20had%20zero%20association%20with%20her%20birth%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20to%20be%20brand%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can't%20be%20based%20off%20my%20birth%20name%20or%20anything%20I've%20done%20with%20JLM.%20They%20are%20a%20part%20of%20my%20past%2C%20and%20this%20is%20my%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Gutman's%20decision%20to%20change%20her%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJLM%20posted%20a%20statement%20about%20the%20lawsuit%20on%20its%20corporate%20Instagram%20account%20on%20March%209%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jlm%20statement%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6047c30e44d8e300117b9e43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20released%20a%20new%20statement.%3Cp%3EJLM%20Couture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20Couture%20took%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMMnxFdjuo1%2F%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20again%20on%20March%209%2C%202021%2C%20to%20make%20a%20general%20statement%20that%20addressed%20both%20the%20court%20ruling%20and%20Gutman's%20most%20recent%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIntellectual%20property%20is%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20every%20modern%20business%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20fashion%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%20%26quot%3BJLM%20takes%20these%20rights%20very%20seriously%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20employment%20agreement%20clearly%20and%20unambiguously%20set%20out%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20obligations%2C%20what%20rights%20were%20being%20acquired%20and%20what%20restrictions%20would%20be%20imposed%20on%20Ms.%20Gutman%2C%20all%20of%20which%20she%20freely%20and%20knowingly%20agreed%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20JLM%20will%20never%20deny%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20talent%2C%20JLM%20rejects%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20accusations%20as%20well%20as%20her%20version%20of%20business%20ethics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20went%20on%20to%20say.%20%26quot%3BMs.%20Gutman%20testified%20in%20court%20that%20she%20does%20not%20believe%20that%20a%20material%20omission%20is%20a%20form%20of%20a%20lie.%20JLM%20does%20not%20subscribe%20to%20that%20version%20of%20'business%20ethics'%20or%20how%20she%20is%20trying%20to%20mislead%20the%20public%20about%20the%20facts%20or%20the%20case%20or%20her%20own%20motivations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20her%20public%20statements%20Ms.%20Gutman%20omits%20the%20overwhelming%20evidence%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20that%20these%20social%20media%20accounts%20were%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20Hayley%20Paige%20brand%20business%20and%20marketing%20strategy%2C%20and%20were%20run%20as%20such%2C%20including%20admissions%20to%20that%20effect%20in%20her%20own%20emails%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20Gutman%20hadn't%20told%20her%20followers%20that%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Bsecretly%20licensed%26quot%3B%20her%20name%20to%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20so%20she%20could%20do%20business%20through%20him%20and%20avoid%20the%20terms%20of%20her%20contract.%20The%20statement%20also%20noted%20that%20Gutman%20used%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20accounts%20to%20promote%20Chosen%20Foods%20and%20Optimum%2C%20which%20violated%20her%20contract%20with%20JLM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20does%20not%20subscribe%20to%20her%20version%20of%20business%20ethics%20where%20consumers%20and%20followers%20are%20misled%20and%20not%20given%20the%20facts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20court%20considered%20all%20of%20the%20actual%20evidence%20and%20facts%20in%20the%20case%2C%20it%20rejected%20her%20arguments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20strongly%20encourages%20anyone%20interested%20in%20this%20case%20to%20read%20the%20court's%20entire%20decision%20and%20reach%20their%20own%20conclusions%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20a%20link%20to%20the%20court%20decision%20to%20the%20bio%20of%20its%20Instagram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20responded%20to%20JLM's%20Instagram%20post%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20on%20March%209%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hpg%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6047d25b2db4af00117e460a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20responded%20to%20JLM%20via%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2Fallthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20told%20Business%20Insider%20via%20email%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20changes%20in%20my%20life%20and%20moving%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20asked%20for%20comment%20on%20JLM's%20post.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20I%20am%20changing%20my%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20Couture%20is%20a%20company%20that%20relies%20entirely%20on%20women%20for%20its%20business%2C%20but%20it%20continues%20to%20treat%20women%20with%20utter%20disrespect%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20went%20on%20to%20say.%20%26quot%3BJLM%20took%20control%20of%20my%20social%20media%20and%20never%20informed%20the%20followers%20of%20these%20accounts%20that%20they%20are%20speaking%20with%20a%20corporation%2C%20not%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20has%20also%20turned%20off%20comments%20on%20both%20my%20social%20media%20channels%20and%20their%20own%2C%20which%20is%20both%20deceptive%20and%20disrespectful%20to%20the%20thousands%20of%20strong%20women%20who%20have%20shared%20their%20opinion%20about%20JLM's%20actions%2C%20only%20to%20find%20their%20words%20deleted%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20speak%20squelched%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20part%20of%20a%20disrespectful%20pattern%20of%20behavior%20that%20is%20the%20exact%20reason%20I%20started%20working%20towards%20a%20separation%20agreement%20last%20summer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20working%20with%20me%20in%20good%20faith%2C%20they%20ignored%20my%20requests%20while%20they%20were%20secretly%20preparing%20this%20litigation%20to%20take%20from%20me%20by%20force%20what%20they%20could%20not%20get%20any%20other%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20opinion%20of%20those%20who%20have%20communicated%20with%20me%2C%20and%20attempted%20to%20communicate%20with%20them%2C%20I%20believe%20they%20have%20made%20a%20terrible%20mistake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20believed%20that%20my%20social%20media%20accounts%20belonged%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20started%20my%20Instagram%20account%20on%20my%20own%20accord%20and%20shared%20a%20deeply%20personal%20view%20into%20my%20life.%20I%20am%20disappointed%20by%20the%20court's%20temporary%20ruling%2C%20but%20confident%20that%20the%20ultimate%20outcome%20will%20be%20favorable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20interim%2C%20I%20am%20moving%20forward%20with%20my%20life%20and%20my%20creative%20passions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BChanging%20my%20name%20is%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20a%20new%20future%2C%20but%20it%20is%20certainly%20not%20the%20last.%20Stay%20tuned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20filed%20a%20counterclaim%20against%20JLM%20Couture%20and%20CEO%20Joe%20Murphy%20on%20March%2022%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221019%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F605a52e5106eb50019d05388%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22764%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20filed%20a%20counterclaim.%3Cp%3EEugene%20Gologursky%20%2F%20Contributor%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2022%2C%202021%2C%20Gutman%20filed%20a%20counterclaim%20against%20JLM%2C%20denying%20many%20of%20the%20company's%20allegations%20against%20her%2C%20including%20that%20she%20misused%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20was%20able%20to%20review%20the%20counterclaim%2C%20which%20contained%20new%20allegations%20against%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20counterclaim%2C%20Gutman%20said%20that%20JLM%20withheld%20compensation%20from%20her%20in%20the%20form%20of%20both%20her%20base%20pay%20and%20additional%20compensation%20she%20said%20she%20was%20supposed%20to%20receive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20claim%20said%20that%20JLM%20%26quot%3Bwillfully%20failed%20to%20pay%20and%2For%20unlawfully%20deducted%20the%20Additional%20Compensation%20due%20to%20Hayley%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20past%20six%20years.%20The%20amount%20of%20money%20Gutman%20said%20was%20withheld%20from%20her%20was%20redacted%20in%20the%20copy%20of%20the%20counterclaim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20counterclaim%20also%20said%20that%20JLM%20defamed%20Gutman%20in%20private%20and%20public%20following%20her%20departure%20from%20the%20company%20in%20December.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20counterclaim%20argued%20that%20JLM's%20claim%20that%20Gutman%20changed%20the%20passwords%20on%20her%20social-media%20accounts%20following%20the%20Temporary%20Restraining%20Order%20isn't%20true%20and%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20defame%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20also%20sued%20the%20CEO%20of%20JLM%20Couture%2C%20Joe%20Murphy%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20company%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20created%20a%20hostile%20work%20environment%20for%20her%2C%20made%20sexually%20inappropriate%20comments%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bengaged%20in%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20other(s).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20counterclaim%2C%20Gutman%20alleged%20that%20Joe%20Murphy%20sexually%20harassed%20JLM%20employees.%20JLM%20denied%20the%20allegations%20in%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IMG_2994%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F605a0bce106eb50019d051bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20accused%20Murphy%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%20JLM%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2Fallthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20counterclaim%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BJLM%20forced%20Hayley%20to%20endure%20a%20workplace%20of%20fear%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20inappropriate%20behavior%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20Murphy's%20leadership.%20JLM%20denied%20these%20allegations%20in%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20calling%20the%20claims%20%26quot%3Bfictitious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20alleged%20that%20women%20who%20had%20romantic%20relationships%20with%20Murphy%20were%20given%20preferential%20treatment%2C%20such%20as%20more%20flexible%20work%20hours.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20counterclaim%20said%20that%20Gutman%20knew%20of%20at%20least%20three%20romantic%20relationships%20Murphy%20had%20with%20women%20who%20were%20his%20subordinates%2C%20including%20a%20sexual%20relationship%20in%20which%20Murphy%20apparently%20fathered%20a%20child%20while%20he%20was%20married%20to%20someone%20else.%20While%20most%20employees%20were%20not%20named%20in%20the%20counterclaim%2C%20it%20mentioned%20one%20woman%20%E2%80%94%20who%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20had%20a%20sexual%20relationship%20with%20Murphy%20%E2%80%94%20by%20name.%20The%20employee%20named%20in%20the%20counterclaim%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20on%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20counterclaim%20said%20that%20Murphy%20would%20put%20down%20women%20who%20rejected%20him.%20For%20instance%2C%20Gutman%20said%20that%20Murphy%20made%20negative%20comments%20about%20a%20female%20JLM%20employee's%20boyfriend%20and%20critiqued%20her%20work%20to%20Gutman%20after%20the%20employee%20had%20denied%20his%20advances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20counterclaim%20said%20Murphy%20told%20Gutman%20over%20text%20messages%20that%20the%20employee%20who%20rejected%20him%20%26quot%3Bis%20put%20together%20differently%20psychologically%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20micromanaged%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bcan't%20delegate%20%5B...%5D%20has%20no%20aptitude%2C%20cannot%20keep%20track%20of%20time%20nor%20multitask.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20counterclaim%2C%20Murphy's%20inappropriate%20behavior%20was%20well%20known%20throughout%20the%20company%20and%20often%20occurred%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Gutman%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BMurphy%20commented%20on%20an%20intern's%20blouse%20and%20said%2C%20'I%20didn't%20know%20it%20was%20a%20wet%20T-shirt%20day'%20in%20front%20of%20other%20JLM%20employees%26quot%3B%20on%20one%20occasion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20also%20said%20that%20Murphy%20made%20sexist%20comments%20about%20motherhood%20to%20her%2C%20saying%20that%20employees%20who%20had%20children%20%26quot%3Bwere%20performing%20poorly%20because%20of%20their%20familial%20status.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20counterclaim%2C%20Gutman%20said%20that%20Murphy%20harassed%20her%20on%20multiple%20occasions.%20JLM%20also%20denied%20these%20allegations%20in%20its%20statement.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IMG_2996%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F605a0c0d0d155e0019ef632b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20alleged%20Murphy%20sexually%20harassed%20her.%20JLM%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2Fallthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20counterclaim%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20Murphy%20directly%20harassed%20Gutman%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20made%20inappropriate%20comments%20about%20her%20body%20on%20multiple%20occasions.%20JLM%20also%20denied%20these%20allegations%20in%20its%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20saying%20that%20Gutman%20%26quot%3Bwas%20always%20treated%20with%20the%20utmost%20respect%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20counterclaim%20said%20that%20Murphy%20compared%20Gutman%20to%20a%20JLM%20employee%20he%20was%20dating%2C%20invited%20her%20to%20his%20Florida%20beach%20house%20for%20a%20recreational%20trip%2C%20and%20made%20her%20feel%20physically%20unsafe%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMurphy%20would%20often%20summon%20Hayley%20to%20a%20crammed%20secluded%20back%20office%2C%20use%20his%20physically%20imposing%20nature%20to%20block%20the%20door%2C%20and%20engage%20in%20inappropriate%20and%20invasive%20personal%20conversations%20into%20Hayley's%20romantic%20relationships%2C%20sex%20life%2C%20and%20family%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20counterclaim%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20meetings%2C%20according%20to%20the%20counterclaim%2C%20Murphy%20encouraged%20Gutman%20to%20discuss%20her%20relationship%20with%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20then%20told%20her%20that%20her%20relationship%20was%20%26quot%3Breally%20not%20good%20for%26quot%3B%20her%20as%20it%20distracted%20her%20from%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20counterclaim%20said%20that