0name%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20went%20on%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20years%2C%20Ms.%20Gutman%20was%20the%20highest-compensated%20employee%20of%20JLM%20Couture%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%20%26quot%3BJLM%20denies%20claims%20by%20Ms.%20Gutman%20regarding%20a%20hostile%20work%20environment%20or%20that%20Ms.%20Gutman%20was%20harassed%20or%20mistreated%20in%20any%20way.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20she%20was%20always%20treated%20with%20the%20utmost%20respect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJLM%20announced%20Francesca%20Pitera%20would%20be%20designing%20a%20new%20line%20of%20Hayley%20Paige%20gowns%20on%20April%209%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221959%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Francesca%20Pitera%20is%20designing%20new%20gowns%20for%20Hayley%20Paige%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6093015534af8d001859b796%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221470%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrancesca%20Pitera.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2F%40jlm_couture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20made%20the%20announcement%20on%20the%20JLM%20Couture%20Instagram%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHappy%20Fri-YAY%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thrilled%20to%20announce%20that%20new%20Hayley%20Paige%20gowns%20are%20coming%20your%20way%20soon%20by%20our%20new%20lead%20designer%2C%20Francesca%20Pitera.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20shared%20a%20sneak%20peek%20at%20the%20new%20Hayley%20Paige%20capsule%20collection%20on%20its%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComments%20were%20disabled%20on%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJLM%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Gutman%20and%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20on%20May%203%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20and%20fiance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F605a53570d155e0019ef6516%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Conrad%20Louis%2C%20Gutman's%20fianc%C3%A9.%3Cp%3ESlaven%20Vlasic%20%2F%20Stringer%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjlm-couture-suing-hayley-paige-gutman-fiance-name-2021-5%5C%22%3EJLM%20filed%20a%20new%20complaint%20against%20Gutman%20and%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20Conrad%20Louis%20Clevlen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20Conrad%20Louis%20on%20social%20media%2C%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%2C%20which%20Business%20Insider%20reviewed%2C%20accused%20the%20couple%20of%20copyright%20infringement%2C%20breach%20of%20contract%2C%20defamation%2C%20and%20other%20charges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20Clevlen%20helped%20Gutman%20breach%20her%20contract%20with%20JLM%20by%20facilitating%20the%20use%20of%20her%20name%20by%20companies%20like%20Optimum%20Nutrition%2C%20Inc.%20without%20JLM's%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20complaint%20said%20that%20Clevlen%20%26quot%3Ballowed%20Gutman%20to%20receive%20payments%20through%20his%20contract%26quot%3B%20with%20Optimum%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20do%20business%20behind%20JLM's%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20JLM%20spokesperson%20provided%20Business%20Insider%20with%20a%20screenshot%20of%20an%20email%20in%20which%20Gutman%20told%20an%20Optimum%20staff%20member%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20to%20have%20all%20payments%20go%20through%20Conrad's%20contract.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20also%20accused%20Gutman%20of%20defamation%2C%20saying%20in%20the%20complaint%20that%20her%20Instagram%20videos%20about%20the%20legal%20issues%20between%20herself%20and%20the%20company%20had%20impacted%20business.%20The%20complaint%20said%20Gutman's%20videos%20had%20led%20at%20least%2050%20bridal%20stores%20to%20stop%20working%20with%20JLM%20and%2035%20stores%20to%20rescind%20orders%20from%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20asked%20for%20a%20tr