m%20Instagram%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20said%20Gutman's%20actions%20violated%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20because%20%26quot%3Bwhile%20the%20Court%20modified%20its%20order%20to%20clarify%20that%20Ms.%20Gutman%20was%20enjoined%20from%20the%20identified%20competitive%20actions%20'%5Bu%5Dntil%20August%201%2C%202022'%20it%20did%20not%20give%20Ms.%20Gutman%20%3Cem%3Eaffirmative%3C%2Fem%3E%20permission%20to%20design%20under%20a%20different%20name.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%20to%20say%20that%20JLM's%20contract%20with%20Gutman%20prevented%20her%20from%20working%20or%20designing%20for%20brands%20that%20competed%20with%20JLM%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20element%20of%20the%20contract%20had%20yet%20to%20be%20discussed%20in%20the%20legal%20proceedings%20between%20the%20company%20and%20Gutman%2C%20and%20BI's%20previous%20coverage%20of%20Gutman's%20plans%20to%20create%20a%20new%20brand%20noted%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20her%20new%20launch%20was%20dependent%20on%20future%20litigation%20with%20JLM%2C%20not%20just%20the%20preliminary%20injunction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20then%20listed%20seven%20demands%20of%20Gutman%20by%20June%2021%2C%20including%20removing%20the%20video%20from%20June%207%20from%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20account%20and%20issuing%20a%20public%20retraction%20about%20the%20new%20brand%20both%20on%20Instagram%20and%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20extent%20these%20issues%20are%20not%20resolved%20immediately%2C%20JLM%20will%20be%20seeking%20relief%20from%20the%20Court%2C%20which%20will%20include%20equitable%20relief%20ordering%20the%20above%20as%20well%20as%20damages%20available%2C%20including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20sanctions%20for%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20contempt%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20removed%20the%20video.%20However%2C%20she%20did%20not%20issue%20a%20retraction%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20posted%20the%20letter%