JLM%20stands%20behind%20its%20positions%20in%20the%20letter%20sent%20to%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20counsel.%20The%20letter%20was%20a%20good%20faith%20attempt%20to%20resolve%20the%20issues%20to%20avoid%20having%20to%20make%20a%20motion%20for%20contempt%2C%20including%20asking%20that%20the%20videos%20be%20taken%20down%20and%20Ms.%20Gutman%20issue%20corrective%20statements%20on%20Instagram%20and%20with%20Insider.com%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMs.%20Gutman%20has%20refused%2C%20instead%20electing%20to%20further%20try%20to%20incite%20ill-will%20towards%20JLM%20Couture%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20went%20on%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20Couture%20will%20be%20seeking%20relief%20from%20the%20Court%20and%20will%20be%20filing%20a%20motion%20for%20contempt%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20July%2015%2C%202021%2C%20JLM%20officially%20filed%20a%20motion%20to%20hold%20Gutman%20in%20contempt%20of%20court.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20sits%20in%20a%20room%20with%20windows%20and%20looks%20off%20into%20the%20distance.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60f6f4121f6c450011ada531%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20motion%20was%20filed%20on%20July%2015.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2F%40allthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20filed%20the%20motion%20and%20a%20memorandum%20of%20law%20to%20explain%20the%20motion%2C%20which%20Business%20Insider%20was%20able%20to%20review.%20The%20memo%20cited%20Gutman's%20social-media%20use%20and%20comments%20to%20the%20media%2C%20including%20Business%20Insider%2C%20as%20violations%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20issued%20against%20her%2C%20saying%20she%20was%20building%20a%20base%20of%20support%20for%20her%20new%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3BGutman's%20clear%20and%20admitted%20intent%20is%20to%20use%20the%20time%20the%20non-compete%20is%20in%20effect%20to%20market%20and%20promote%20the%20brand%2C%20build%20her%20consumer%20base%20and%20design%20her%20collection%2C%20so%20that%20her%20dresses%20can%20go%20on%20sale%20with%20a%20built-in%20customer%20base%20the%20day%20her%20non-compete%20ends%26quot%3B%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM's%20memo%20said%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20video%20in%20which%20Gutman%20announced%20she%20would%20be%20launching%20a%20new%20brand%20under%20a%20new%20name%20next%20year%20was%20a%20form%20of%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20cited%20comments%20under%20the%20video%20from%20brides%20who%20said%20they%20planned%20to%20buy%20from%20Gutman's%20new%20line%20as%20evidence%20that%20her%20content%20violated%20the%20preliminary%20injunction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20also%20cited%20a%20%3Ca%20data-uri%3D%5C%22e6d9ca061ae7692e770b52e6bbb047cc%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhayley-paige-to-launch-brand-new-name-in-august-2022-2021-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0about%20the%20new%20line%20that%20featured%20exclusive%20comments%20from%20Gutman%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20fact%20that%20Gutman%20shared%20the%20story%20to%20Instagram%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bswipe%20up%26quot%3B%20feature%2C%20as%20evidence%20of%20the%20violation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20the%20exact%20type%20of%20competitive%20harm%20that%20the%20non-compete%20provision%20was%20intended%20to%20prevent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20motion%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20memo%20also%20cited%20sketches%20Gutman%20shared%20to%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20Instagram%20as%20evidence%20of%20her%20violation%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221981%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20an%20Instagram%20reel%20of%20a%20woman%20drawing%20a%20sketch%20of