ar%20as%20to%20delete%20prior%20negative%20comments%20about%20their%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20combination%20with%20this%20latest%20effort%20to%20use%20the%20courts%20to%20avoid%20public%20opinion%2C%20it's%20clear%20that%20JLM%20is%20suffering%20great%20harm%20from%20the%20litigation%20they%20started.%20They%20have%20no%20one%20but%20themselves%20to%20blame%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20representative%20went%20on%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20reiterated%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20motion%20for%20contempt%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20Couture%20Inc.%20was%20forced%20on%20July%2015%20to%20seek%20relief%20in%20Federal%20Court%20after%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20continuous%20flagrant%20violations%20of%20Judge%20Laura%20Taylor%20Swain's%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20JLM%20said.%20%26quot%3BMs.%20Gutman%20was%20asked%20to%20stop%20violating%20Judge%20Swain's%20order%20and%20to%20take%20down%20the%20infringing%20videos%20and%20posts%20%E2%80%93%20but%20she%20refused.%20This%20left%20JLM%20Couture%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20seek%20immediate%20relief%20from%20the%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMs.%20Gutman's%20video%20released%20this%20morning%20continues%20to%20promote%20a%20false%20and%20misleading%20narrative%20with%20reference%20to%20the%20contempt%20motion%20itself%20and%20the%20interactions%20between%20the%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20went%20on%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20said%20JLM's%20actions%20didn't%20%26quot%3Bsurprise%26quot%3B%20her%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20surprise%20me%20that%20JLM%20continues%20to%20blame%20me%20instead%20of%20acknowledging%20the%20impact%20of%20its%20own%20actions%3B%20and%20that%20JLM%20continues%20to%20want%20to%20silence%20and%20restrain%20me%20instead%20of%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20move%20forward%20in%20a%20professional%2C%20business-minded%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20contempt%20motion's%20vitriol%20speaks%20for%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20was%20held%20in%20contempt%20of%20court%20on%20September%208%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20wears%20a%20black%20hat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F613a6657a30aeb0018b4ca56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20judge%20found%20Gutman%20was%20in%20contempt%20of%20court.%3Cp%3EEugene%20Gologursky%20%2F%20Contributor%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJLM's%20request%20to%20hold%20Gutman%20in%20contempt%20was%20partially%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20stated%20in%20a%20memorandum%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20court%20found%20that%20Gutman%20was%20marketing%20her%20upcoming%20brand%20with%20her%20posts%20and%20comments%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20Because%20her%20future%20brand%20would%20directly%20compete%20with%20JLM%2C%20it%20was%20ruled%20that%20Gutman's%20posts%20and%20comments%20put%20her%20in%20willful%2C%20civil%20contempt%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20issued%20in%20March.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Csection%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20decided%20that%20Gutman%20was%20enjoined%20from%20%26quot%3Bannouncing%20a%20new%20brand%20name%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20present%20or%20future%20commercial%20venture%20involving%26quot%3B%20bridal%20wear%2C%20bridal%20accessories%2C%20evening%20wear%2C%20or%20any%20other%20products%20sold%20by%20JLM%20until%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20expired%20in%20August%20of%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20memorandum%2C%20Gutman%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20JLM's%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20attorneys'%20fees%20and%20costs%26quot%3B%20because%20she%20violated%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20also%20ordered%20to%20delete%20Instagram%20posts%20from%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20post%20related%20to%20her%20plans%20for%20a%20new%20brand%20from%20May%207%2C%20June%207%2C%20June%2021%2C%20June%2025%2C%20and%20July%2015%2C%202021%2C%20within%20five%20days%20of%20the%20ruling%2C%20as%20stated%20in%20the%20memorandum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20shared%20the%20news%20on%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20account%20on%20September%209%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221678%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20a%20post%20on%20Instagram.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F613a649f2534ab00185398b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221078%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20posted%20about%20the%20ruling%20on%20Instagram.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2F%40allthatglittersonthegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Csection%20data-track-content%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-post-type%3D%5C%22post%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20former%20employer%2C%20JLM%20Couture%2C%20sought%20and%20was%20granted%20a%20contempt%20order%20against%20me%20in%20Federal%20Court%20which%20requires%20that%20I%20delete%20several%20videos%20and%20posts%20that%20I%20have%20made%20here%20on%20Instagram%20by%20September%2013%2C%202021%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20wrote%20in%20her%20post.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20apologize%20to%20those%20of%20you%20who%20poured%20your%20heart%20and%20time%20into%20comments%20on%20these%20videos%20and%20posts.%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%20your%20support%2C%20and%20your%20love%2C%20and%20I%20want%20you%20to%20know%20that%20I%20love%20everyone%20of%20you%20right%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20September%209%2C%20Gutman%20had%20not%20deleted%20every%20post%20required%20from%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20account%2C%20though%20some%20of%20them%20appeared%20to%20have%20been%20removed%20at%20the%20time.%20As%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20they%20were%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20said%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20matter%20when%20contacted%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%20on%20September%209%2C%202021%2C%20a%20JLM%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BJLM%20is%20pleased%20with%20the%20outcome%20of%20this%20decision%2C%20although%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20it%20has%20come%20to%20this.%20The%20Court%20issued%20a%20clear%20PI%20based%20upon%20the%20rights%20and%20provisions%20that%20Ms.%20Gutman%20voluntarily%2C%20knowingly%2C%20and%20intelligently%20agreed%20to%2C%20which%20Ms.%20Gutman%20has%20flagrantly%20violated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20repeatedly%20tried%20to%20obtain%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20compliance%20before%20making%20this%20motion%2C%20but%20Ms.%20Gutman%20refused%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20went%20on%20to%20say.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20JLM's%20hope%20that%20Ms.%20Gutman%20will%20respect%20her%20contractual%20obligations%20and%20the%20Court's%20Orders%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Csection%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20reflected%20on%20one%20year%20of%20legal%20battles%20with%20JLM%20Couture%20on%20December%2014%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20an%20Instagram%20post%20from%20%40allthatglittersonthegram.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61b8d1a01f225d0018d90d0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222709%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20posted%20on%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20on%20December%2014%2C%202021.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2F%40allthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2014%2C%20Gutman%20marked%20the%20one-year%20anniversary%20of%20the%20start%20of%20her%20legal%20issues%20with%20JLM%20couture%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCXeF_aaFSe7%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dshare_sheet%5C%22%3Ean%20Instagram%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20one%20year%20since%20I%20was%20sued%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20by%20the%20employer%20I%20dedicated%20over%209%20years%20of%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20fearing%20or%20caving%20in%2C%20I%20stood%20up%20for%20myself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20then%20went%20on%20to%20catalog%20the%20legal%20entanglements%20that%20ensued%20between%20her%20and%20JLM%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20including%20her%20recent%20decision%20to%20appeal%20her%20case%20to%20the%20Second%20Circuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20in%20the%20post%20that%20her%20ongoing%20legal%20battle%20with%20JLM%20%26quot%3Bdrained%20me%20financially%20of%20all%20the%20money%20I%20ever%20made%20as%20a%20designer%20and%20most%20of%20my%20life%20savings%2C%20while%20continuing%20to%20profit%20from%20my%20designs%20and%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20finished%20the%20post%20by%20thanking%20her%20followers%20and%20asking%20them%20to%20share%20her%20message%2C%20signing%20the%20post%20as%20%26quot%3BA%20Girl%20You%20Might%20Know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20July%2025%2C%202022%2C%20the%20court%20denied%20Gutman's%20motion%20to%20dissolve%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20and%20modified%20part%20of%20the%20injunction%20in%20JLM's%20favor.%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22instagram%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22instagram%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCf16s41Pphf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%3Ctime%20datetime%3D%5C%22undefined%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ftime%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGutman's%20request%20to%20dissolve%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20was%20denied%20in%20a%20memorandum%20order%20in%20July%202022%2C%20meaning%20she%20was%20still%20prevented%20from%20using%20any%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts%20or%20trademarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20opinion%20and%20order%20modifying%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20also%20stated%20Gutman%20would%20be%20able%20to%20work%20in%20the%20bridal%20industry%20or%20any%20other%20industry%20that%20competes%20with%20JLM%20Couture%20starting%20on%20August%201%2C%202022%3B%20however%2C%20she%20could%20not%20be%20%26quot%3Bidentified%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20designer%20or%20use%20her%20identity%20to%20promote%20the%20sales%20of%20a%20business%20in%20competition%20with%20JLM%20Couture%20until%20August%201%2C%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20while%20Gutman%20could%20theoretically%20work%20as%20a%20designer%20for%20another%20label%2C%20that%20brand%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20use%20her%20fame%20to%20sell%20dresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20pleased%20that%20the%20Court%20continues%20to%20uphold%20the%20'clear%20and%20unambiguous'%20language%20of%20the%20employment%20contract%20that%20provided%20with%20Ms.%20Gutman%20with%20generous%20compensation%20as%20well%20as%20complete%20financial%20and%20infrustructural%20backing%20for%20the%20Hayley%20Paige%20brand%20and%20afforded%20her%20exclusive%20opportunities%20for%20fame%20and%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20JLM%20said%20of%20the%20rulings%20in%20a%20press%20release%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20designer%20announced%20she%20had%20changed%20her%20name%20to%20Cheval%20on%20August%208%2C%202022.%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22instagram%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22instagram%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FChACWE-Iy5O%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%3Ctime%20datetime%3D%5C%22undefined%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ftime%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20designer%20announced%20her%20new%20name%20in%20a%20video%20on%20Instagram%20in%20August%202022%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-dress-designer-hayley-paige-changed-her-name-cheval-2022-8%5C%22%3Espoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20exclusively%20%3C%2Fa%3Eabout%20why%20she%20chose%20Cheval%2C%20which%20means%20%26quot%3Bhorse%26quot%3B%20in%20French.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%C2%A0stumbled%20upon%20the%20name%20Cheval%20organically%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20some%20of%20her%20business%20mentors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20at%20a%20place%20that%20had%20the%20name%20Cheval%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20always%20been%20somebody%20that's%20been%20drawn%20to%20imaginary%20unicorns%20and%20imaginative%20mindsets.%20And%20horses%20kind%20of%20always%20represented%20something%20of%20fortitude%20and%20strength%20and%20this%20idea%20of%20running%20against%20the%20wind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20felt%20immediately%20drawn%20to%20Cheval%20as%20a%20real%20name%20and%20an%20identity%20that%20I%20could%20step%20into%20and%20feel%20really%20proud%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20her%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheval%20also%20said%20using%20one%20name%20felt%20right%20because%20of%20many%20of%20the%20artists%20she%20looks%20up%20to%2C%20like%20Adele%20and%20Beyonce%CC%81.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChoosing%20something%20that%20is%20just%20one%20name%20felt%20like%20I%20could%20harness%20the%20energy%20and%20power%20that%20I%20want%20to%20carry%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20launched%20a%20shoe%20brand%20to%20accompany%20the%20name%20called%20She%20Is%20Cheval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJLM%20Couture%20filed%20for%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%20in%20a%20Delaware%20court%20on%20October%202%2C%202023.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221771%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pen%20on%20top%20of%20a%20paper%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BChapter%2011%20Bankruptcy.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6656298f20abc1efe8fe2c23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy.%3Cp%3EFuzzMartin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20file%20for%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%2C%20companies%20can%20restructure%20with%20government%20assistance%20rather%20than%20selling%20their%20assets%20to%20appease%20debtors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fjlm-couture-inc-announces-financial-225900080.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20bankruptcy%20filing%2C%20JLM%20said%20Gutman%20was%20among%20the%20reasons%20it%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20primary%20motivators%20for%20this%20decision%20stems%20from%20external%20challenges%20including%20the%20actions%20of%20Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20and%20pressure%20from%20legacy%20creditors%2C%20including%20potential%20liability%20stemming%20from%20New%20York%20City%20landlord-tenant%20issues%20aggravated%20by%20the%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reviewed%20JLM's%20bankruptcy%20filing%2C%20which%20Joe%20Murphy%20signed%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Second%20Circuit%20vacated%20a%20portion%20of%20JLM's%20preliminary%20injunction%20against%20Gutman%20in%20January%202024.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hayley%20Paige%20smiles%20in%20a%20black%20dress%20in%20front%20of%20a%20white%20and%20pink%20backdrop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66562b85239fda2da6cc403b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221503%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHayley%20Paige%20in%202018.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Webber%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20The%20Pink%20Agenda%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20filed%20another%20appeal%20of%20the%20New%20York%20District%20Court's%20preliminary%20injunction%20ruling%20against%20her%20in%20September%202023%20to%20the%20Second%20Circuit%20Court%20of%20Appeals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2017%2C%20the%20Second%20Circuit%20vacated%20a%20modification%20the%20New%20York%20District%20Court%20made%20of%20JLM's%20preliminary%20injunction.%20The%20modification%20had%20given%20JLM%20exclusive%20control%20of%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20Second%20Circuit%20said%20the%20District%20Court%20should%20have%20viewed%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20accounts%20as%20property%20when%20analyzing%20the%20case%2C%20which%20would%20have%20altered%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20analysis%20of%20social-media-account%20ownership%20begins%20where%20other%20property-ownership%20analyses%20usually%20begin%E2%80%94by%20determining%20the%20account's%20original%20owner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20stated.%20%26quot%3BThe%20next%20step%20is%20to%20determine%20whether%20ownership%20ever%20transferred%20to%20another%20party.%20If%20a%20claimant%20is%20not%20the%20original%20owner%20and%20cannot%20locate%20their%20claim%20in%20a%20chain%20of%20valid%20transfers%2C%20they%20do%20not%20own%20the%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20Second%20Circuit%20vacated%20that%20part%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%2C%20the%20New%20York%20District%20Court%20had%20to%20look%20at%2