ruptcy%20filing%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20suggests%20that%20the%20Debtor's%20financial%20state%20is%20over%20%243.4%20million%20worse%20than%20expected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20told%20BI%20in%20May%20that%20she%20saw%20bankruptcy%20court%20as%20a%20way%20to%20approach%20her%20issues%20with%20JLM%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20a%20different%20perspective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20really%20seeing%20litigation%20as%20a%20place%20where%20there%20were%20going%20to%20be%20winners%20and%20losers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20it%20as%20almost%20like%20an%20infinite%20game.%20So%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'I%20need%20to%20choose%20a%20new%20path.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Apil%2030%2C%20JLM%20objected%20to%20the%20motion%20in%20a%20separate%20filing%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Motion%20should%20be%20denied%20as%20a%20transparent%20effort%20by%20a%20former%20employee%20to%20push%20her%20own%20agenda%20of%20destroying%20the%20Debtor%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20all%20creditors%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20filing%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20May%208%2C%20the%20New%20York%20District%20Court%20ordered%20JLM%20to%20reinstate%20Gutman's%20access%20to%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hayley%20Paige%20sits%20on%20a%20pink%20ottoman%20wearing%20fluffy%20shoes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66561ff3a961b37edf3a74bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20District%20Court%20modified%20its%20ruling.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memorandum%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20New%20York%20District%20Court%20dissolved%20and%20modified%20sections%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20modification%20JLM%20was%20granted%