C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Nellore%2C%20Suhas%20moved%20away%20from%20home%20for%20education.%20%E2%80%9CI%20moved%20to%20different%20cities%20for%20my%20senior%20schooling%20and%20graduation.%20I%20had%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20away%20from%20home%20that%20I%20had%20this%20longing%20to%20be%20back%20in%20my%20hometown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20my%20PhD%20in%20pharmacy%2C%20I%20decided%20that%20it%20was%20time%20for%20me%20to%20move%20back%20and%20stay%20closer%20to%20my%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20move%20also%20meant%20that%20I%20had%20to%20look%20for%20different%20avenues%20of%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20a%20humble%20background%20and%20setting%20up%20my%20own%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F190337%2Fprafulla-chandra-ray-father-indian-chemistry-history-science-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epharma%20company%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20outlet%20in%20Nellore%20was%20not%20a%20possibility.%20While%20I%20had%20never%20thought%20actively%20about%20entrepreneurship%2C%20it%20was%20along%20the%20way%20that%20I%20realised%20that%20it%20might%20be%20my%20calling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Suhas%20moved%20back%20home%20in%202013%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20he%20had%20something%20in%20abundance%20%E2%80%94%20access%20to%20pure%20milk.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20big%20cities%2C%20pure%20and%20organic%20milk%20can%20be%20very%20expensive%2C%20but%20here%2C%20I%20could%20buy%20it%20for%20as%20low%20as%20Rs%2055.%20I%20decided%20to%20think%20in%20that%20direction%20and%20it%20dawned%20on%20me%20that%20an%20ice%20cream%20business%20might%20flourish%20in%20Nellore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsuhas-1-1716901930.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20uses%20Mishri%2C%20a%20natural%20sweetener%20instead%20of%20sugar%20in%20the%20icecream.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsuhas-1-1716901930.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsuhas-1-1716901930-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsuhas-1-1716901930-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsuhas-1-1716901930-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsuhas-1-1716901930-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351376%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20uses%20Mishri%2C%20a%20natural%20sweetener%20instead%20of%20sugar%20in%20the%20icecream.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Suhas%E2%80%99%20grandparents%20made%20icecreams%20when%20he%20was%20a%20kid.%20%E2%80%9CAlmost%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20they%20had%20a%20small%20local%20icecream%20business.%20My%20inspiration%20also%20comes%20from%20them.%20Initially%2C%20I%20turned%20to%20their%20recipes%20and%20knowledge%20to%20start%20my%20manufacturing%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20main%20ingredient%20used%20in%20making%20icecream%20available%20to%20him%20in%20abundance%20and%20his%20grandparents%E2%80%99%20recipes%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20open%20a%20small%20outlet%20and%20shop%20in%20Nellore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20made%2045%20litres%20of%20icecream%20and%20within%20two%20days%20of%20opening%20the%20store%2C%20the%20icecreams%20were%20sold%20out.%20The%20sales%20were%20quite%20organic%3B%20word%20spread%20around%20the%20town%20and%20we%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20visiting%20the%20shop.%20I%20had%20to%20close%20my%20shop%20for%20one%20day%20and%20increase%20production.%20On%20the%20fifth%20day%2C%20we%20came%20with%20double%20the%20stock%20and%20have%20never%20looked%20back%20since%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20making%20great%20sales%20and%20opened%20another%20shop%20in%20Nellore.%20Within%20three%20years%2C%20I%20have%20established%20more%20than%2015%20stores%20across%20South%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20quick%20to%20get%20into%20the%20B2B%20business%20of%20franchising%20his%20icecream%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%20the%20company%20makes%20six%20to%20seven%20lakh%20litres%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345217%2Fbest-ice-cream-parlours-places-mumbai-snowman-taj-icecream-haji-ali-gokul-rustom-naturals-bachelorr%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eicecream%20every%20month.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESwitch%20to%20organic%20icecreams%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Suhas%20was%20making%20good%20profits%2C%20the%20work%20began%20to%20feel%20monotonous.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20reinvesting%20all%20the%20earnings%20from%20my%20business%20back%20into%20the%20same%20model.%20However%2C%20I%20soon%20realised%20that%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20direction%20I%20wanted%20for%20my%20business.%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20more%3B%20a%20satisfaction%20that%20I%20was%20doing%20something%20good.%20I%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20food%20business%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20sustainable%20and%20organic%20living%20was%20being%20circulated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20realised%20that%20it%20might%20be%20the%20right%20time%20to%20switch%20and%20give%20people%20an%20alternative%20to%20regular%20icecreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20not%20target%20the%20market%20for%20organic%20icecreams%3F%E2%80%99%20Considering%20the%20popularity%20of%20organic%20products%20like%20biscuits%2C%20%3Cem%3Enamkeen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20even%20%3Cem%3Eagarbatti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20opportunity.%20There%20are%20even%20brands%20for%20organic%20smokes%2C%20so%20why%20not%20icecream%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20the%20company%20started%20producing%20organic%20icecreams.%20%E2%80%9CRegarding%20the%20product%2C%20we%20majorly%20focus%20on%20the%20ingredients.%20We%20use%20only%20the%20desi%20cow%20milk%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20have%20set%20up%20my%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20a%20tier%202%20town%20like%20Nellore.%20In%20larger%20cities%2C%20this%20milk%20is%20sold%20at%20approximately%20Rs%20150%20per%20litre%2C%20but%20in%20tier%202%20cities%2C%20I%20can%20get%20it%20for%20Rs%2050%20to%2060%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20awareness%20and%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20strategy%20allows%20him%20to%20achieve%20sustainable%20business%20growth%20by%20utilising%20local%20materials%20and%20cutting%20cost%2C%20he%20informs.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20replace%20sugar%20with%20%3Cem%3Emishri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20natural%20sweetener%2C%20in%20our%20icecream.%20We%20use%20organic%20butter%20and%20vegetable-extracted%20colours.%20Importantly%2C%20we%20do%20not%20use%20any%20preservatives%20or%20stabilisers%20in%20our%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20a%20product%20called%20edible%20gum%2C%20also%20called%20%3Cem%3Egondh%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20a%20preservative.%20We%20have%20developed%20a%20process%20to%20use%20%3Cem%3Egondh%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20a%20preservative%20ingredient%20in%20our%20icecream.%20This%20ingredient%20is%20organic%20and%20helps%20us%20achieve%20an%20average%20shelf%20life%20of%20six%20to%20eight%20months%2C%20