ince%20childhood.%20She%20took%20inspiration%20from%20her%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20Bishnois%2C%20and%20love%20for%20the%20environment%20is%20in%20our%20DNA.%20We%20are%20known%20for%20our%20drive%20to%20save%20wild%20animals%20and%20trees%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20famous%20Chipko%20movement.%20My%20mother%20instilled%20in%20us%20the%20value%20of%20being%20a%20conservationist%20and%20planting%20more%20trees%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20marriage%2C%20Sharda%20decorated%20her%20home%20with%20as%20many%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20easier%20for%20anyone%20to%20distinguish%20our%20home%20from%20others%20as%20I%20have%20more%20than%201%2C000%20plants.%20However%2C%20while%20raising%20my%20children%2C%20I%20never%20really%20got%20enough%20time%20to%20spend%20time%20in%20gardening%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-2-1716437290.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sharda%20shifted%20her%20focus%20to%20miniature%20tray%20gardens%20as%20it%20allows%20her%20to%20unleash%20her%20creativity.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-2-1716437290.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-2-1716437290-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-2-1716437290-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-2-1716437290-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-2-1716437290-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cf