ould%20once%20gape%20at%20in%20pure%20wonder.%20The%20mammoth%20facade%20blended%20the%20ideas%20of%20Greek%20architects%20Pythius%20and%20Satyros%2C%20with%20sculptures%20flanking%20its%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20beauty%20personified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20palace%20on%20Muktaram%20Babu%20Street%20in%20North%20Kolkata%20(previously%20Calcutta%2C%20the%20seat%20of%20the%20British%20Raj)%2C%20is%20said%20to%20inspire%20the%20same%20reaction.%20While%20people%20have%20pointed%20out%20a%20resemblance%20between%20the%20Marble%20Palace%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20and%20the%20monument%20in%20Turkey%2C%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20any%20sound%20proof%20whether%20the%20latter%20inspired%20the%20former.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20architectural%20emblem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mansion%20that%20fuses%20cultures.%20This%20moniker%20aptly%20describes%20the%20Marble%20Palace%3B%20a%20white%20beacon%20of%20serenity%20set%20against%20a%20bustling%20stretch%20of%20land%20dotted%20with%20shops%20and%20bazaars.%20With%20its%20neoclassical%20architecture%20rising%20to%20the%20skies%20and%20its%20manor-like%20gates%20opening%20up%20a%20portal%20into%20an%20alternate%20dimension%20%E2%80%94%20a%20royal%20one%20if%20you%20will%20%E2%80%94%20the%20palace%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best-preserved%20private%20spaces%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4s4UlKStVk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4s4UlKStVk%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EVie