0impact%2C%20future%2C%20challenges%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20conversation%2C%20IPS%20Rishabh%20also%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20find%20wholehearted%20support%20from%20a%20person%20for%20emotional%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFind%20a%20person%20in%20your%20life%20who%20supports%20you%20in%20this%20journey%20irrespective%20of%20the%20number%20of%20failures%20and%20stays%20with%20you%20like%20a%20bedrock%2C%20cheering%20you%20up%20in%20all%20your%20sorrows.%20Find%20that%20person%20who%20encourages%20you%20even%20when%20you%20lose%20confidence%20in%20yourself%20%E2%80%94%20the%20one%20who%20enjoys%20making%20you%20laugh%2C%20making%20studies%20fun%20rather%20than%20a%20burden%20that%20you%20have%20to%20complete%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Rishabh%20Bhola%20(Instagram).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716550863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FIPS-Rishabh-Bhola-1-1716526732.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351050%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20fourth%20attempt%2C%20IPS%20officer%20Rishabh%20Bhola%20secured%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20410%20in%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%202021.%20He%20shares%20five%20tips%20for%20effective%20note-making%20to%20help%20retain%20and%20review%20information%20during%20revision.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351050%2Fupsc-cse-how-to-make-notes-ips-officer-rishabh-bhola-shares-tips-tricks-techniques%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%2015-YO%20Gold%20Winner%20of%20International%20Robotics%20Contest%20%26amp%3B%20a%20Student-Teacher%20Bond%20Behind%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHow%20far%20will%20a%20teacher%20go%20to%20guarantee%20her%20student%E